title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Mar 18 2022

description:
Buck explains Biden's Title 42 border dilemma. What will happen if Biden ends Trump's wise order? The Fauch (with Buck doing his spot-on impression) reappears to tell us it's not over. Pandemia author Alex Berenson joins Buck, drops bomb about the negative efficacy of the vaccines against Omicron. Austria returns to indoor mask mandate two weeks after dropping it. Buck predicts blue states will stop-start Fauciism.
